{"title":"点·线·面","authors":["朱相远"],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":10,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"点·线·面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朱相远"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个点，向前移动只成一条线；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一根线，向前移动就成一个面。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一部犁走过，翻起一垅土；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一排犁走过，翻起一大片。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"单种经营是一垅土，一条线；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农、林、牧、副、渔，多种经营齐向前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成了面，一大片，公社收入万万千。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}